Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, March 16 (XINHUA) -- Luo Gan, Chinese 
State Councillor and secretary-general of the State Council, met 
with visiting Thai Minister of Justice Sawai Phatthano and his 
party here today. 
  Sawai and his entourage arrived here yesterday. This 
afternoon, an agreement of judicial assistance in civil and 
commercial matters and cooperation in arbitration between China 
and Thailand was signed here by Chinese Minister of Justice Xiao 
Yang and Sawai Phatthano. 

